                    <div id="glossary" class="block2 block">
                        <div class="text">
                            API - Application Programming Interface<br>
                            ISF - Integrated Semantic Framework<br>
                            LOD - Linked Open Data<br>
                            MeSH - Medical Subject Headings<br>
                        </div>
